WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.933 --> 00:00:13.666
Come on, Kiki, you see that you like sweet potatoes the most.

2
00:00:15.066 --> 00:00:18.666
Dad, I'm home for Chinese New Year, and my mom blocked me.

3
00:00:18.666 --> 00:00:21.566
Why don't you give him a call and tell him to go home?

4
00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:28.266
Hello dad

5
00:00:28.300 --> 00:00:30.333
I've been waiting outside for five hours

6
00:00:30.333 --> 00:00:31.600
When will my mom be back?

7
00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:32.866
It's still freezing outside

8
00:00:32.866 --> 00:00:36.666
Oops, your mom has something to do at a friend's house today

9
00:00:37.066 --> 00:00:38.366
Can't come back for the time being

10
00:00:38.366 --> 00:00:41.600
The dishes cooked by the couple's aunt are so fragrant, come and eat

11
00:00:42.500 --> 00:00:44.233
Hey let me tell you

12
00:00:44.266 --> 00:00:46.800
You find a hotel for a few days

13
00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:49.866
Xiao Yang is fine, don't call me, okay?

14
00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:56.600
Aunt and uncle are in good health and all the best

15
00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:59.266
Touch one, come on, come on

16
00:00:59.300 --> 00:01:01.700
Hahahaha

17
00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:03.700
Eat fast, eat well, it's so hot

18
00:01:11.900 --> 00:01:13.166
My aunt loves me very much

19
00:01:13.166 --> 00:01:15.166
He said he didn't want to go home and get back together

20
00:01:15.166 --> 00:01:16.833
Just want to be with me

21
00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:21.066
It's what you call passing by again

22
00:01:22.500 --> 00:01:24.766
I really hope you guys don't come back until after Chinese New Year.

23
00:01:25.333 --> 00:01:27.100
So you can see me

24
00:01:27.566 --> 00:01:29.033
Dead body

25
00:01:48.533 --> 00:01:51.833
I wish my aunt and uncle good health and all the best.

26
00:01:51.866 --> 00:01:53.200
Touch a good one

27
00:02:06.300 --> 00:02:07.500
Look at him.

28
00:02:15.666 --> 00:02:17.500
You-you shouldn't have given up on treatment

29
00:02:17.500 --> 00:02:20.100
If you give up now, the cancer will spread rapidly

30
00:02:20.100 --> 00:02:21.766
In less than three months, I will

31
00:02:24.733 --> 00:02:25.533
Mr. Chen

32
00:02:26.333 --> 00:02:27.766
I won't eat it.

33
00:02:28.200 --> 00:02:31.066
My mother still wants to wait for me to come home for Chinese New Year

34
00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:34.100
I want to spend my last days with her

35
00:02:34.366 --> 00:02:37.200
Mom and Dad

36
00:02:37.600 --> 00:02:38.900
I forgive you.

37
00:02:39.600 --> 00:02:42.300
I only allowed you to have me for half a month

